elements.name: Mobile Withdrawal transaction verification(OW Sports, Dafa Sports, Casino, Casino Gold, Common Wallet and PT+)

steps.name: the player is at Dafabet mobile site in "en" language
the player logs in using "QAAUTOTRANSACT" credentials
the player is on the Cashier page
the player checks the balance before for "OW Sports"
the player navigates to "Withdrawal" menu in mobile Cashier page
choose "Local Bank Transfer" Payment option
the player performs withdrawal in mobile "OW Sports", "1000.00"
the player navigates to "History" menu in mobile Cashier
need to wait for countdown of "50000"
"Withdrawal" transaction and "1000.00" and "Cancel" information are retrieved in mobile
